article_text:
Write a news story about the voting rights bill (HB1901). You may choose to write about one or more of the following:
• the history of the Voting Rights Act of 1965;
• why Republicans in the State Legislature are against the bill;

• what the bill does;
o what it does to protect minority voting rights;
or
• anything else you think is important about the bill.

Please include a link to the text of the bill (see below) in your news article.
https://www.azleg.gov/legtext/54leg/1r/bills/hb2550s.pdf

You may use the following news article as a guide.
http://www2.tuscon.com/news/local/politics/arizona-politics-in-perspective-voting-rights-bill-on-the-line/article_1e94496b-84e5-59b1-a9c3-1d2676e5f823.html
